Interface SqmExpressionInterpretation<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DomainResultProducer
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AssignableNavigableReference, NavigableContainerReference, NavigableReference, TableGroup
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTableGroup, BasicValuedNavigableReference, CteTableGroup, EmbeddableValuedNavigableReference, EntityValuedNavigableReference, IdTableGroup, StandardTableGroup, TableGroupJoin

    public interface SqmExpressionInterpretation<T>
extends DomainResultProducer
    The interpretation of an SqmExpression as part of the SQM -> SQL conversion. Allows multi-column navigable references to be used anywhere a (SqlExpression) can be. The trick is to properly define methods on this interface for how the thing should be rendered into the SQL AST.
